tourBios.otherCarHigh: Won the 2008 Frank Landry Invitational. Was an All-American Scholar in 2011 and 2012.
tourBios.personal: Lists biggest thrill in golf as holing out for eagle to win a playoff to qualify for the U.S. Amateur in 2011...Fan of the Baltimore Ravens and Baltimore Orioles. Grandfather Jack Dunn is in the Orioles' Hall of Fame...Dream foursome would include his dad, Jesus Christ and Babe Ruth...Favorite course is Merion.

dyn.dynBios: Grandfather Jack Dunn is in the Baltimore Orioles Hall of Fame
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T24th in 2014 at the The Players Cup.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 82nd in Scoring Average (Actual) on the PGA TOUR Canada.
